main.game.object.champion.champions.ezreal

Class EzrealE

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.game.object.GameObject
      • main.game.object.spell.Spell
        • main.game.object.champion.champions.ezreal.EzrealE

  • public class EzrealE
extends Spell
    This class contains the methods for Ezreal's Spell E, since this is a special case. It is not just a Spell that should be fired; nothing is fired, but the character is teleported.
    Author:
    ikhebgeenaccount 17 sep. 2015
